      <p>HeroesToo Foundation is a registered Hong Kong charity established in July 2010 dedicated to restoring and protecting our environment.</p>
      <p>By engaging and empowering the public through school, community, and corporate programmes, we believe each and every one of us has the power to take action and save the planet.</p>
      <hr>
      <p>We support the UN Global Citizen Campaign to achieve the UN’s Global Goals to take action on sustainability, global health and climate change.</p>
      <p>We are an affiliate member of the Hong Kong Business Environment Council engaging with various stakeholders in promoting Hong Kong’s environmental sustainability.</p>
      <hr>
      <p>Our HeroesToo EcoPledge Education Program enables us to successfully collaborate with schools, reaching out to students with our holistic ‘whole school’ sustainable lifestyle education process enabling eco-friendly habits to be formed.</p>
      <p>With the EcoPledge Education Program and the individual EcoPledge action, we educate, empower and connect individuals and institutions to create new habits, reducing waste of the earth’s resources, enabling a lasting response to environmental threats. We channel this collective energy to make meaningful impact in saving our environment.</p>
      <p>We can expand our Programmes to make the impact needed now only with much needed funding from from businesses and institutions.</p>
